files.description: The sole EHI export documentation artifact. A 4-page PDF (cover + 3 pages) describing the export structure: a ZIP per patient containing a C-CDA XML file (clinical data), a documents folder (scanned/uploaded files in original formats), and a Patient Documents Detail.xls index file. Version 1.0, dated November 2023. No data dictionary, schema, or field-level documentation. Created with Microsoft Word.

Screenshot of the data-export landing page showing the 'Data Export' banner heading and a single link labeled 'Electronic Health Information Export Documentation' pointing to the PDF. No other content on the page.
